Stills and publicist work together with marketing teams to help get the project out there and noticed. When I first moved to ATL I got a random call from a producer and asked if I could FaceTime with a director for a project. Of course agreed and @williamhmacy was FaceTime with me. I was only 27 and was told he loved my black and white work. When I got off that call I had to recap all the things that just happened and who I talked to. Few weeks later I was on set with several amazing cast and crew (#BillMacy @rosariodawson #williamfichtner #cathybates #tiharris @imrickafox @therealnickrobinson @grantgust etc) was such a great way to start out life in ATL. And was def a jumping point in my career. Did the stills and a little gallery shoot that ended being put together for the #Poster / #OneSheet thank you Bill and everyone that worked on this passion project! #unitphotography #unitstills #setphotographer #bts #publicity #moviestills #keyart #photogallery #movieposter #filmcrew #joshstringer #filmstring #unitpublicist #producer #director #atlantaphotographer #californiaphotographer #celebrityphotographer #newyorkphotographer #headshotcrew #theheadshotguy #celebrityphotographer #commercialphotographer #advertising

It’s an Irish kinda day (happy St patty’s) but wanted to combo today with Ireland and Hawaii. Why? Bc we have been getting ALOT of amazing people from #hawaii coming to the studio in ATL! Everyone from the islands have been amazing with their energy, large hearts and big laughs. Just wanted to shout out the first that came in and got shots with us ever in atl is my buddy @adenstaykauai he was referred by @nickdekay and ever since we have been like brothers (not just bc I look like a mini version of him) but bc of his huge heart and constant support professionally and personally cheering me and our people on. Wish all the good things to this big lug, to his family and friends! He’s an islander but also yes being we look very much alike he has a little Irish to his blood. So let’s all be like Islanders and eat, drink, sing a song, to you and yours, thank you for the love here there and wherever we may roam.
